Name: MotoGP™15 Compact
About the game: Riders, teams and tracks from the MotoGP™ 2015 season brought together in a unique, essential and comprehensive videogame. Experience all the thrills of real two-wheel racing with the MotoGP™15 Compact: choose from the official riders and tracks in the MotoGP™ 2015 category. Different game modes: Grand Prix, Championship and Split Screen, as well as the Online Grand Prix to challenge your friends! No excuses: become a MotoGP™ rider and put your skills to the test on the track!
